### ============================================================================
### Ticket Controller Tests
### ============================================================================

### GET All Tickets
GET {{host}}/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### GET Ticket by ID
GET {{host}}/api/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### POST Create a Ticket (Multipart/FormData via HTTP Client can be tricky, here is a representation)
POST {{host}}/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ticket"; filename="blob"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceId": 1,
  "title": "Projector not working in Room A",
  "description": "The projector screen won't turn on and the bulb seems dead."
}
--boundary--

### PUT Update Ticket Status
PUT {{host}}/api/tickets/1/status?status=IN_PROGRESS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PUT Resolve Ticket
PUT {{host}}/api/tickets/1/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resolutionNotes": "Replaced the bulb. Projector works now."
}

### ============================================================================
### Booking Controller Tests
### ============================================================================

### GET All Bookings Check
GET {{host}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### GET Bookings By User ID
GET {{host}}/api/bookings/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### GET Booking By ID
GET {{host}}/api/bookings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### POST Create Booking
POST {{host}}/api/bookings?userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceId": 2,
  "startTime": "2026-03-08T10:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-03-08T12:00:00",
  "purpose": "Weekly Team Meeting"
}

### PUT Update Booking Status
PUT {{host}}/api/bookings/1/status?status=APPROVED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### DELETE Cancel Booking
DELETE {{host}}/api/bookings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### Resource Controller Tests
### ============================================================================

### GET All Resources
GET {{host}}/api/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### GET Filtering Resources (Example: type=MEETING_ROOM)
GET {{host}}/api/resources?type=MEETING_ROOM
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET Resource By ID
GET {{host}}/api/resources/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST Create Resource
POST {{host}}/api/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Conference Room A",
  "type": "MEETING_ROOM",
  "location": "Building 1, Floor 2",
  "capacity": 20,
  "description": "Large conference room with projector and whiteboard."
}

### PUT Update Resource
PUT {{host}}/api/resources/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Conference Room A (Updated)",
  "type": "MEETING_ROOM",
  "location": "Building 1, Floor 2",
  "capacity": 25,
  "description": "Large conference room with new Apple TV.",
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

### DELETE Delete Resource
DELETE {{host}}/api/resources/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### Notification Controller Tests
### ============================================================================

### GET My Notifications
GET {{host}}/api/notifications?userId=1&unreadOnly=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### PUT Mark Notification as Read
PUT {{host}}/api/notifications/1/read?userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PUT Mark All Notifications as Read for User
PUT {{host}}/api/notifications/read-all?userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
